<h2>Verify Your Email Address</h2>

<p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

<p>Welcome to EventFlow! To complete your registration and start discovering amazing events, please verify your email address.</p>

<div class="info-box">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1e40af;">Your Verification Code</h3>
    <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; font-family: monospace; color: #1e40af; margin: 20px 0;">
        {{verificationCode}}
    </p>
    <p class="text-muted" style="text-align: center;">This code expires in {{expiryMinutes}} minutes</p>
</div>

<a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>

<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
    <span class="text-muted">Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</span><br>
    <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" style="color: #1e40af; word-break: break-all; font-size: 12px;">{{verificationUrl}}</a>
</p>

<div class="divider"></div>

<h3 style="color: #1e40af;">Why Verify Your Email?</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Secure your account and prevent unauthorized access</li>
    <li>Receive order confirmations and ticket updates</li>
    <li>Get notifications about your favorite events</li>
    <li>Reset your password if you forget it</li>
</ul>

<div class="info-box" style="background-color: #fef3c7; border-left-color: #f59e0b;">
    <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Didn't create an account?</strong></p>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0;">If you didn't sign up for EventFlow, you can safely ignore this email. The verification link will expire automatically.</p>
</div>

<p class="text-muted">
    Having trouble? Contact our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>
</p>
